_sText:
Studio: BigBox Studios.
More from Shaz: http://www.knology.net/~shaunburch/shaz.html


This is my third production. DE_Servers, formerly dubbed Project_1, is finally complete. De_servers is a office-style map, with features like radar, soundscapes, spot and dynamic lighting, enviornment cubemaps, tweaked navigation for effective bots, and a secret room. It has a blend of sniper advantage spots and close quaters combat.


File Size: 869 kb
File Type: .rar
Maximum Players: 32
